---
title: "_call (WorkflowRouter via Caller)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_call: (success, response) = target.call(data)
    q_call --> q_check_success: check success
    q_check_success --> q_success: success == true
    q_success --> [*]: return response
    q_check_success --> q_check_response: success == false
    q_check_response --> q_bubble_revert: response.length > 0
    q_bubble_revert --> [*]: revert with response data (bubble up)
    q_check_response --> q_low_level_fail: response.length == 0
    q_low_level_fail --> [*]: revert LowLevelCallFailed()

    note right of q_call
        INV-001: low-level call forwards all remaining gas
        INV-002: if target reverts with data, the revert reason is bubbled up
        INV-003: if target reverts without data, LowLevelCallFailed is thrown
        INV-004: return value is the raw bytes from the external call
    end note
